&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 staff nurse to join our friendly, ever developing Same Day Emergency Care service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SDEC is a consultant led unit with support from an ACP team and is a great place to consider working if you feel you may want to develop into a career of Advanced Clinical Practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SDEC sees a wide range of patients from A&amp;E and GP’s with a wide range of medical conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The staff nurse will be expected to work closely within the team in the delivery of dynamic excellent care. The successful candidates need to possess excellent communication skills, be highly motivated and committed to patient safety and improving patient experience. They will need to have drive and an ability to manage their workloads in a challenging, fun and developing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to the nature of the post-extended skills such as IV additives, IV cannulation, Phlebotomy, ECG’s and catheterisation are essential criteria.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work flexibly doing 11.5hr shifts over a 5 day week.&lt;/p&gt;
